        "geocode_query": "16363 E Fremont Ave",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post IMT Cornerstar Ranch Address: 16363 E Fremont Ave Aurora, CO 80016 Base monthly rent: $1874 - $1999 Mandatory monthly fees: $39.00 Total Monthly Price: $1913.00 - $2038.00 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Bedrooms: 2 | Baths: 2 | Sq. Footage: 1106 sq ft | Terms: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Reach out via phone: show contact info LOOK & LEASE: Receive 2 months free rent when you apply within 24 hours of your tour.* *Restrictions apply; offer subject to change at any time. Offer expires on 06/29/26. Special offer only applies to base rent and not any fees included in Total Monthly Price. Credit will apply to the second full month's statement. Special excludes all property transfers and current residents. 12-month minimum lease term applies. + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + Features in this apartment home: ◾ Built-In Desks & Shelving in Select Homes ◾ Cable Ready ◾ Central Heating & Air Conditioning ◾ Fully Equipped Kitchen ◾ In-Home Washer/Dryers ◾ Pantry ◾ Plush Carpet in Bedrooms ◾ Private Patio or Balcony ◾ Spacious Walk-In Closets ◾ Breakfast Bar in Select Homes ◾ Detached Garages & Select Carports Available ◾ Dual Vanity in Select Homes ◾ Fireplaces in Select Homes ◾ Garden Tub ◾ Kitchen Islands in Select Two Bedroom Homes ◾ Nine-Foot Ceilings ◾ Spectacular Mountain Views in Select Homes + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + Amenities at our property: ◾ 24-Hour Package Lockers ◾ Emergency Maintenance Service ◾ IMT Active ◾ IMT CoWork ◾ On-Site Car Wash ◾ On-Site Storage Available ◾ Resort-Style Pool & Spa with Poolside Games Lawn, Lounge & Sundeck ◾ Two IMT Pets Parks ◾ Valet Trash ◾ Adjacent to Cherry Creek Valley Ecological Park with Miles of Trails & Sweeping Views of the Rocky Mountain Front Range ◾ Convenient Access to E-470, Denver Technological Center, Meridian Business District, Denver International Airport, Fitzsimons, Downtown Denver & Buckley Air Force Base ◾ Direct Access to 42-Mile Cherry Creek Trail ◾ Located in Highly Coveted Cherry Creek School District ◾ My IMT Resident Portal with Online & On-Site Kiosk Access: Utilities Connection, Rent Payment, Service Requests, Account Information & Community Postings ◾ Nearby Running/Bike Path ◾ Next to Cornerstar Shopping Center & Arapahoe Crossings, with a Variety of Restaurant, Retail & Entertainment Options ◾ Sand Volleyball Court ◾ Ten minutes from Park Meadows Mall, Colorado's Largest Indoor Shopping Mall + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + About the community: **Walk-ins welcome & choose from 3 tour options.** IMT Cornerstar Ranch is comprised of one-, two- and three-bedroom apartment homes located in Aurora, CO. Each home includes an array of interior amenities from fully equipped gourmet kitchens and garden tubs to in-home washer/dryers and spacious walk-in closets. Community amenities include a sand volleyball court, a resort-style pool, and a playground. IMT Cornerstar Ranch is pet friendly with an elite dog park with an agility course. Take a Virtual Tour of Our Property Today! https://liveimt.com/imtCornerstarRanchYoutubeTour Price shown is Total Monthly Price including monthly mandatory fees* Mandatory Fees: - Package Locker: $5/month - Credit Reporting: $5/month - Trash Administrative Fee: $3.88/month - Submetered Water: Varies - Submetered Sewer: Varies - Submetered Gas: Varies - Valet Trash Service: $25/month Pets: At IMT Cornerstar Ranch, we know that the path to your heart is marked with paw prints and that the best part of your day is coming home to a wagging tail. Pets are residents too! - TWO PET MAXIMUM - NO WEIGHT RESTRICTIONS, BREED RESTRICTIONS APPLY - $300 PET DEPOSIT PER HOME - $35 MONTHLY PET FEE PER HOME Reach out via phone: show contact info Hours: Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sat: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM Sun: 12:00 PM - 5:00 PM Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/imtCornerstarRanch/ Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=imt_cornerstar_ranch&rp=iAmvGksQe56j&t=wb Online Application: www.apts-rental.com?n=imt_cornerstar_ranch&rp=iAmvGksQe56j&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=imt_cornerstar_ranch&rp=iAmvGksQe56j&t=trt *Total Monthly Price includes base rent, all monthly mandatory and any user-selected optional fees. Excludes variable, usage-based, and required charges due at or prior to move-in or at move-out. Discounts, if applicable, will be calculated upon lease execution. Minimum lease terms and occupancy guidelines may apply. Deposits may vary based on credit, rental history, income, or other qualifying criteria. Additional fees and taxes may apply and will be disclosed per governing laws and company policies. Total Monthly Price may be displayed as a whole dollar amount for advertising purposes only; actual charges are calculated using exact fee amounts, including cents, and may vary from the displayed amount by up to 50 cents due to rounding. Mandatory Fees: - Package Locker: $5/month - Credit Reporting: $5/month - Trash Administrative Fee: $3.88/month - Submetered Water: Varies - Submetered Sewer: Varies - Submetered Gas: Varies - Valet Trash Service: $25/month Portable Tenant Screening Report Advisement: 1) Applicant has the right to provide an IMT Residential managed community with a Portable Tenant Screening Report (PTSR) that is not more than 30 days old, as defined in § 38-12-902(2.5), Colorado Revised Statutes; and 2) if Applicant provides IMT Residential with a PTSR, IMT is prohibited from: a) charging Applicant a rental application fee; or b) charging Applicant a fee to access or use the PTSR. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY EJGB106VL46G1Z0",
