vide Outpost on Yukon with a Portable Tenant Screening Report (PTSR) that is not more than 30 days old, as defined in § 38-12-902(2.5), Colorado Revised Statutes; and 2) if Applicant provides Outpost on Yukon with a PTSR, Outpost on Yukon is prohibited from: a) charging Applicant a rental application fee; or b) charging Applicant a fee for Outpost on Yukon to access or use the PTSR. Equal Housing Opportunity zNe9KfdL2",
